item.title: Steering Committee Meeting
item.description: The original committees from Tama and Toledo, and others who wish to join the effort, are invited to meet and discuss organization, priorities, and next steps. This meeting will be held in the Toledo Public Library. Agenda specifics: Will be posted as soon as they are available. Check back here often.
